history.content:
Hi,

I'm a rising senior trying to enroll in EE 16A and during my phase 1, in addition to adding myself to the waitlist for the class, I added myself to the waitlist for Discussion Section 999 and Lab Section 107 (Tuesday 5-8pm in Cory 140).

However, it looks like Section 107 is no longer in the course guide (on both CalCentral and guide.berkeley.edu). I was wondering if that would affect my ability to get off the waitlist because from my understanding, students have to be able to get off both the waitlist for the Lecture component of the course and the waitlist of any supplemental sections of the course (in EE16A's case it would just be the Lab section's waitlist).

Thank you!
